  <acqinfo id="aspace_c189809ba7b2cf9c33b9d6745906a62d">
    <head>Immediate Source of Acquisition</head>
<p>Donated by Theodore Bonin in December, 2016; the accession number associated with this gift is 2017.031.</p>  </acqinfo>
