  <arrangement id="aspace_3329d7d6800acaaabe80d6ef8851e227">
    <head>Arrangement</head>
<p>Materials have been intellectually arranged in the inventory by an archivist following the donor's alphabetical list by artists' last name, followed by publications. Physically the material was boxed together according to size.</p>  </arrangement>
  <processinfo id="aspace_12445c99f8d68476d3d0b6c63c824491">
    <head>Processing Information</head>
<p>Materials were foldered, wrapped in appropriate packing material, and placed in boxes according to their size. Descriptions for works were taken from the donor-created list and reformated for the finding aid.</p>  </processinfo>
  <bioghist id="aspace_c03ac1c9d343b6bb60c7db3eed9d755e">
    <head>Biographical Note</head>
<p>Theodore Bonin is an art collector and part owner of Alexander and Bonin, a New York art gallery established in 1995, whose primary purpose is to represent and support the work of emerging, mid-career, and established international contemporary artists.</p>  </bioghist>
